com.google.gwt.dev.util.log.dashboard
Interface DashboardNotifier

All Known Implementing Classes:
NoOpDashboardNotifier
public interface DashboardNotifier

Sends information to a dashboard service. The dashboard service collects information from GWT runtime and compiler instrumentation.
